<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1956-03-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1956-03-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="537" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d537">
                        <head>537. Telegram 1754 to Geneva<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d537fn1">Source: Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/3–1356. Secret;
                                Priority; Limit Distribution. Drafted by <persName corresp="#p_CRN_1">Clough</persName>; cleared by Phleger and
                                    <persName corresp="#p_MWP_1">McConaughy</persName>. Repeated
                                Priority to Saigon for <persName corresp="#p_RWS_1">Robertson</persName> as Tosec 70.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1956-03-13">March 13, 1956, 6:55
                                    p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <pb facs="d537-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d537-1"/>
                        <p>1754. For <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName>.</p>
                        <p>National Catholic Welfare Conference has learned from letters sent by
                            Father Houle to his mother that he was tried October 30, 1955 and
                            sentenced 4 years retroactive to date of arrest June 1953.</p>
                        <pb facs="0910" n="863" type="typeset" xml:id="pg_863"/>
                        <p>Without citing Father Houle’s letters as source inform <persName corresp="#p_WP_1">Wang</persName> you have learned of his sentencing
                            and protest in strongest terms this further flagrant violation Agreed
                            Announcement.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_HH_1"><hi rend="strong">Hoover</hi></persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>